"Rasta":
"This is Rasta, come in.
...Ah, I got through."
"Ratel and Rooikat have returned. They're both safe and sound."
"Hey, sorry about all that. Rooikat just headed back to the city ahead of me."
"Man, he had you out looking for me? My bad! I didn't think they'd sent out the cavalry just cause I went home early."
"I'm sorry for putting you to so much trouble. Everything seems to be fine now, so please return as soon as you can."
